WEBVTT

01:07:07.131 --> 01:07:10.714
"The irritation is overwhelming,
yet so charming,"

01:07:11.881 --> 01:07:16.631
"It whispers gibberish in my ears."

01:07:17.339 --> 01:07:20.839
"Honestly, the girl is amazing!"

01:07:22.423 --> 01:07:25.714
"It hurts to be apart from her,
even for a second."

01:07:27.256 --> 01:07:31.381
"I'm losing my sanity in her presence."
